1
00:00:01,060 --> 00:00:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're canceling the operation!</i></font>

2
00:00:02,360 --> 00:00:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Retreat!</i></font>

3
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I repeat!</i></font>

4
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're canceling the operation! Retreat!</i></font>

5
00:00:08,610 --> 00:00:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're kidding me, John!</font>

6
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're canceling the operation! Retreat!</font>

7
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're canceling the operation! Retreat!</i></font>

8
00:00:17,700 --> 00:00:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Retreat!</font>

9
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All hands, retreat!</font>

10
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Slaughterer of chaos...</font>

11
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did not think I could exert
this much power against a human.</font>

12
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:45,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are willing to call me a human...</font>

13
00:00:45,770 --> 00:00:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even though I am in this guise?</font>

14
00:00:48,650 --> 00:00:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Appearance is trivial.</font>

15
00:00:51,650 --> 00:00:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know not your name...</font>

16
00:00:54,370 --> 00:00:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I promise I will engrave
this past battle into my heart.</font>

17
00:00:59,410 --> 00:01:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Master.</font>

18
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shall make the Little Red Riding Hood
burned within you fade.</i></font>

19
00:02:46,890 --> 00:02:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Participate in the Holy Grail War...</i></font>

20
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ayaka Sajyou.</i></font>

21
00:02:51,770 --> 00:02:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you don't want to be devoured
by Little Red Riding Hood.</i></font>

22
00:02:59,450 --> 00:03:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber...</font>

23
00:03:21,850 --> 00:03:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should hide. It's dangerous.</font>

24
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

25
00:03:25,270 --> 00:03:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As Master of the King of Heroes,</font>

26
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a duty to continue
watching him to the very end.</font>

27
00:03:34,110 --> 00:03:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do not have many elements
that allow me to reach you.</font>

28
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

29
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it comes to speed, I can win!</font>

30
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ex...</i></font>

31
00:03:49,290 --> 00:03:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>calibur!</i></font>

32
00:03:51,210 --> 00:03:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How naive!</font>

33
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Excalibur!</i></font>

34
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Excalibur!</i></font>

35
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ex...</i></font>

36
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>calibur!</i></font>

37
00:04:11,230 --> 00:04:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why you little...</font>

38
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ex...</i></font>

39
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>calibur!</i></font>

40
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss, is your body feeling all right?</font>

41
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

42
00:04:33,290 --> 00:04:35,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come to think of it,
I might be feeling a little sluggish.</font>

43
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"A little"?</font>

44
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss...</font>

45
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What...</font>

46
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>are </i>you?</font>

47
00:04:47,810 --> 00:04:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsubaki Kuruoka's room is the rightmost
one from our viewpoint on the top floor.</font>

48
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Much appreciated.</font>

49
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave the rest to me.</font>

50
00:04:56,570 --> 00:04:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, wait a minute.</font>

51
00:05:03,110 --> 00:05:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go with you.</font>

52
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've made a wise choice, boy.</font>

53
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say earlier...</font>

54
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if you had left this lovely lady behind
and retreated by yourself...</font>

55
00:05:24,470 --> 00:05:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would have carved your heart out,
crushed it, kneaded it with sand...</font>

56
00:05:29,470 --> 00:05:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and scattered it into the slop
for pigs to feed on!</font>

57
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you really made the worst choice.</font>

58
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I will never allow
a diminutive human...</font>

59
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}to even attempt walking
alongside my beloved!</font>

60
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Envelop in the black blades...</i></font>

61
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Zabani—</i></font>

62
00:05:55,210 --> 00:05:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jester Karture.</font>

63
00:05:57,380 --> 00:05:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many bullets...</font>

64
00:05:59,250 --> 00:06:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are left within you?</font>

65
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you.</font>

66
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd you get intel on me?</font>

67
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, Mr. Jack?</font>

68
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master...</font>

69
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You transported a half-dead Heroic Spirit?</font>

70
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are likely the only fool
who would use a Command Spell for this.</font>

71
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we defeat that person, will Mr. Ja...</font>

72
00:06:40,550 --> 00:06:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Berserker's Spirit Origin revive?</font>

73
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jack is fine now.</font>

74
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see it, don't you?</font>

75
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

76
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Spirit Origins have fused within him.</font>

77
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's as if they melted together...</font>

78
00:06:53,470 --> 00:06:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">inside something that looks like mud.</font>

79
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:58,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid that even if you defeat him...</font>

80
00:06:58,150 --> 00:07:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my power will not return to me.</font>

81
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:06,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not unless I truly disappear
and then get resummoned from the Throne.</font>

82
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if we do so, will that Mr. Jack
be a different person than you are now?</font>

83
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

84
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right there, whoever it is!</font>

85
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh brother.</font>

86
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't make an
author do physical labor.</font>

87
00:07:24,090 --> 00:07:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Dumas.</font>

88
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alexandre Dumas.</font>

89
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever heard of me?</font>

90
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:32,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? Why would a Heroic Spirit
disclose his True Name—</i></font>

91
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Mr. Dumas? Which one?</font>

92
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The general under Napoleon?</font>

93
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or the author of <i>The Three Musketeers</i>?</font>

94
00:07:39,350 --> 00:07:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, perhaps <i>The Lady of the Camellias</i>?</font>

95
00:07:41,610 --> 00:07:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The second one. You sure know your stuff.</font>

96
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I would know!</font>

97
00:07:47,610 --> 00:07:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I watched the movie, the anime and
the puppet play of <i>The Three Musketeers</i>!</font>

98
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I thank you for that.</font>

99
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're pretty difficult
to figure out, kid.</font>

100
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You jumped into the conversation
while setting up a spell in my shadow.</font>

101
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's definitely a Mage. However...</font>

102
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even when the spell was completed,</font>

103
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you got worked up and kept talking
about <i>The Three Musketeers</i>.</font>

104
00:08:11,140 --> 00:08:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not like a Mage.</font>

105
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I mean, I set it up because I'd be
in danger if you were an enemy.</font>

106
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I executed it and you weren't
an enemy, I'd be wasting Magical Energy,</font>

107
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:24,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it would be bad for you.</font>

108
00:08:25,860 --> 00:08:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, kid,
you don't act like a Mage...</font>

109
00:08:30,450 --> 00:08:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}but are you prepared to throw your life
into a pot for your objective?</font>

110
00:08:45,090 --> 00:08:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is not mere recklessness, either.</font>

111
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, that's...</font>

112
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, you can still move.</font>

113
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ridiculous. Hmm?</font>

114
00:09:12,490 --> 00:09:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mage, you have come out of the cellar.</font>

115
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>P-P-Play Ball!</i></font>

116
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

117
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll leave it up to the boy
whether he does it or not.</i></font>

118
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Jack the Ripper.</i></font>

119
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being able to become anyone
is the best ingredient ever.</i></font>

120
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By mixing that and the boy's presence,
I can fortify your powers temporarily.</i></font>

121
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I can't even imagine what kind
of side effects the Master will have...</i></font>

122
00:09:51,650 --> 00:09:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>after being stewed with a street slasher.</i></font>

123
00:09:56,950 --> 00:09:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh? Is that it?</i></font>

124
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

125
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Musketeers' Masquerade!</i></font>

126
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

127
00:10:14,010 --> 00:10:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Game Select!</i></font>

128
00:10:24,190 --> 00:10:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Running through a part of
Mr. Jack's Noble Phantasm power</font>

129
00:10:26,810 --> 00:10:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you stole is a spell I injected...</font>

130
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that confuses the flow of Magical Energy.</font>

131
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way you can do that—</font>

132
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would have been impossible
unless I got this close.</font>

133
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You could have transformed
into your Master and casted the spell.</font>

134
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would have been the same.</font>

135
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did your Master take the risk
to stand on the battlefield?</font>

136
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because he holds something that I cannot.</font>

137
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Archer's Master has already used up
all the Command Spells, right?</font>

138
00:10:56,130 --> 00:10:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there was even one stroke left,</font>

139
00:10:58,180 --> 00:11:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the power of that connection
would have repelled it.</font>

140
00:11:01,350 --> 00:11:04,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have eyes
that can see through that deeply!</font>

141
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:05,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

142
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not done yet!</font>

143
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this rate—</font>

144
00:11:14,650 --> 00:11:17,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The actor showed some courage.</font>

145
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:21,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes me want to
fix up the logic a bit.</font>

146
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:24,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys like you are the ones...</font>

147
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that should become heroes.</font>

148
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are...</font>

149
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">John!</font>

150
00:12:04,290 --> 00:12:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Game Over.</i></font>

151
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used the Hydra's venom.</font>

152
00:12:12,420 --> 00:12:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

153
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the power given to you
is not a god's blessing.</font>

154
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is a power created
by humans and the earth.</font>

155
00:12:21,470 --> 00:12:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I praise you, my brother...</font>

156
00:12:23,890 --> 00:12:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and...</font>

157
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I pity you, brave hero!</font>

158
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This tainted blood of mine...</font>

159
00:12:30,810 --> 00:12:34,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The flames of revenge
harboring within my soul...</font>

160
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}cannot be stained by a mere deadly poison!</font>

161
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is he about to do?</font>

162
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly are you?</font>

163
00:12:49,540 --> 00:12:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

164
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unusual to be able to supply that
much Magical Energy to a Heroic Spirit.</font>

165
00:12:56,050 --> 00:13:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the very least, you'd have to be
a top-tier Mage to do so.</font>

166
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say that, but I
really don't understand</font>

167
00:13:04,090 --> 00:13:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this Magical Energy stuff to begin with.</font>

168
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss...</font>

169
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What <i>are</i> you?</font>

170
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:19,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was planning on eradicating you,
church and all.</font>

171
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have become curious
about this thing's fate.</i></font>

172
00:13:29,290 --> 00:13:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gilgamesh...</i></font>

173
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You did the same for me once upon a time.</i></font>

174
00:13:35,170 --> 00:13:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You thought of protecting this location?</font>

175
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ought to sneer at your arrogance
and slay you here...</font>

176
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but by nullifying that attack,
you've earned my acknowledgement.</font>

177
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That is...</i></font>

178
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>an honor.</i></font>

179
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber?</font>

180
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can win. We can win...</font>

181
00:14:10,490 --> 00:14:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Gilgamesh!</font>

182
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mongrel...</font>

183
00:14:21,010 --> 00:14:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you hiding within you?</font>

184
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

185
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not talking about your entourage.</font>

186
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm talking about the source
of your own Spirit Origin.</font>

187
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, it appears
you still lack a true reason to fight.</font>

188
00:14:41,570 --> 00:14:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To dare challenge me
while in such an emotional state...</font>

189
00:14:45,990 --> 00:14:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that is flagrant conceit, mongrel.</font>

190
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall execute judgment.</font>

191
00:14:52,830 --> 00:14:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you any final words before I do?</font>

192
00:14:56,290 --> 00:14:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to say I don't, but...</font>

193
00:14:59,590 --> 00:15:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">let's see...</font>

194
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The girl that has provided
my Magical Energy is not a Master.</font>

195
00:15:06,050 --> 00:15:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was one-sided exploitation on my part.</font>

196
00:15:10,100 --> 00:15:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She bares you no hostility,
so please make allowances for her.</font>

197
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

198
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, if I find her existence trivial,
I shall blast her away without hesitation.</font>

199
00:15:21,570 --> 00:15:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No different from the rest of the rabble.</font>

200
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mongrel, the judgment on you—</font>

201
00:15:32,370 --> 00:15:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a tactless act!</font>

202
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came to settle the
score before you died off?</font>

203
00:15:38,710 --> 00:15:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, you thought I could not purify...</font>

204
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that tiny portion of tainted mud?</font>

205
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strong king...</font>

206
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and weak warrior!</font>

207
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:52,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will slaughter you is not that taint!</font>

208
00:15:52,930 --> 00:15:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

209
00:15:53,970 --> 00:15:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is what drowns in that mud!</font>

210
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The corpses!</font>

211
00:15:58,020 --> 00:16:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My distinguished enemy
and pitiful fellow...</font>

212
00:16:02,110 --> 00:16:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you shall dance within my mad rush!</font>

213
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nine Lives!</i></font>

214
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall personally appraise you...</font>

215
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and see how much that hide of yours
recognizes the crafts of humans!</font>

216
00:16:35,350 --> 00:16:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hydra venom, huh?</font>

217
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I already have plenty
of such poison in my stores.</font>

218
00:16:40,850 --> 00:16:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing less from you, my king!</font>

219
00:17:05,090 --> 00:17:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

220
00:17:06,840 --> 00:17:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Holy Grail can even summon
something of this caliber?</font>

221
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

222
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have an interruption.</font>

223
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did not expect you to stray here.</font>

224
00:17:36,660 --> 00:17:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

225
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you have fallen that far...</font>

226
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ishtar, goddess of fertility!</font>

227
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Fallen"? That's quite a
terrible way to say it!</font>

228
00:17:48,210 --> 00:17:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The higher ground I've obtained
hasn't changed from the beginning.</font>

229
00:17:52,510 --> 00:17:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You simply thought
you climbed higher than all of us.</font>

230
00:17:57,470 --> 00:18:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got carried away
and left your Master behind, too!</font>

231
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Holy Grail War isn't
something so easy...</font>

232
00:18:03,690 --> 00:18:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that you could make it through and win
without a united front.</font>

233
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that, right?</font>

234
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More like, you don't feel
the intense pain of the poison yet?</font>

235
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and roll around the ground
to make me laugh!</font>

236
00:18:15,410 --> 00:18:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That arrogance plastered onto your soul
does not dissipate...</font>

237
00:18:19,370 --> 00:18:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even after millennia have passed.</font>

238
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To make me walk through
such a clammy cave alone...</font>

239
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is worth certain death.</font>

240
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A cave...</font>

241
00:18:33,170 --> 00:18:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, thanks to that, I found
something useful in order to kill you.</font>

242
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The key to the vault!</font>

243
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why you...</font>

244
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:47,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's something that is of no use
to an ordinary human.</font>

245
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can lock it up again, at the least.</font>

246
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Closing the door before my treasures
dazzles your eyes...</font>

247
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said you had fallen,
but I stand corrected.</font>

248
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:02,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have become quite laudable!</font>

249
00:19:03,330 --> 00:19:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or...</font>

250
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">did that vessel affect you?</font>

251
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That didn't happen.</font>

252
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This body is a doll that was created
only to become a vessel.</font>

253
00:19:14,670 --> 00:19:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like this little one.</font>

254
00:19:17,430 --> 00:19:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think I made a misjudgment...</font>

255
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are not the actual being,
but an inferior reverberation.</font>

256
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to play around a bit more...</font>

257
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but going further
would make things a bit troublesome.</font>

258
00:19:32,780 --> 00:19:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

259
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps it is the curse itself?</font>

260
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it'd be best to flee.</font>

261
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made an effort
to avoid your vital spots...</font>

262
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you should agonize as long as you can!</font>

263
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or so I'd like to say.</font>

264
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I let it slide...</font>

265
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think this little
guy is so forgiving.</font>

266
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Lord Gilgamesh!
- Lady Tiné!</font>

267
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's dangerous!</font>

268
00:20:35,170 --> 00:20:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

269
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

270
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nooooo!</font>

271
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh brother.</font>

272
00:20:45,010 --> 00:20:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this rate, the audience, the stage...
everything will burn down to cinders.</font>

273
00:20:50,230 --> 00:20:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If so...</font>

274
00:20:51,810 --> 00:20:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should lower the curtains
with my own hands.</font>

275
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be really bad!</font>

276
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber!</font>

277
00:21:04,490 --> 00:21:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry, Ayaka.</font>

278
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was planning on protecting
the church to the end...</font>

279
00:21:11,250 --> 00:21:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I kind of screwed up.</font>

280
00:21:14,380 --> 00:21:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine! Just hurry up
and get your wounds treated!</font>

281
00:21:17,130 --> 00:21:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure the church has
bandages or something!</font>

282
00:21:20,050 --> 00:21:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really aren't a Mage
through and through.</font>

283
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your feelings serve
as a better medicinal herb than bandages.</font>

284
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop joking!</font>

285
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to hurry out of here!</font>

286
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it! Wait!</font>

287
00:21:39,860 --> 00:21:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I made a citizen who I must protect
do such a thing...</font>

288
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would be a disgrace to me
both as a knight and as a king.</font>

289
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the point you're hanging out
with someone like me,</font>

290
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's already been a disgrace
the whole time!</font>

291
00:21:51,290 --> 00:21:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Just hurry up!</font>

292
00:21:53,790 --> 00:21:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And having you
depreciating yourself like that...</font>

293
00:21:58,170 --> 00:22:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}is a disgrace to me as a Heroic Spirit.</font>

294
00:22:07,010 --> 00:22:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 10</font>

